    "Hence, we rely on computational chemistry, employing simulation software and algorithms to model molecule conformers.",
    "Specifically, we utilize the ETKDG algorithm [45] provided by RDKit with default parameters to compute one conformer for each molecule.USPTO-2 is randomly divided into training, validation, and test sets in an 18:1:1 ratio.",
